Requied packages:
libnfnetlink-dev
libnfnetlink0
libnetfilter-queue-dev
libnetfilter-queue1

Recommended packages:
iptables
gzip

Suggeste packages if building on a desktop machine:
dbus
libdbus-1-3
libdbus-1-3-dev

How to build:
git clone git://peerguardian.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/peerguardian/peerguardian
cd peerguardian
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
make install

If you just want certain modules like just pgld do the above but before "make install"
git clone git://peerguardian.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/peerguardian/peerguardian
cd peerguardian
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
cd pgl/pgld
make install

If you just want to build one module like just pgld then cd  to that dir before
creating the build dir:
git clone git://peerguardian.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/peerguardian/peerguardian
cd peerguardian/pgl/pgld
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
make install

Options to cmake for pgld: (syntax: "cmake OPTIONS ..")

-DNODUBS=1
    No DBus support (Auto-detect otherwise)

-DLOWMEM
    Enable LOWMEM support for devices like routers etc
    This disables DBus
